\c 15
\s Jesu pamberi paPirato
\p
\v 1 Pakarepo mangwanani vapristi vakuru vakarangana navakuru navanyori nedare remakurukota rose, vakasunga Jesu, vakamutakura, vaka\add mu\add*kumikidza kuna Pirato.
\v 2 Pirato ndokumubvunza \add achiti\add*: Iwe uri Mambo wavaJudha here? Akapindura, akati kwaari: Unoreva iwe.
\v 3 Vapristi vakuru vakamupomera zvinhu zvizhinji, asi haana kupindura chinhu.
\v 4 Pirato akamubvunzazve achiti: Haupinduri chinhu here? Tarira, zvinhu zvingani zvavanokupomera!
\v 5 Asi Jesu haana kuzopindurazve chinhu, zvokuti Pirato wakashamisika.
\p
\v 6 Zvino pamabiko waivasunungurira musungwa mumwe, chero upi wavanenge vakumbira.
\v 7 Zvino kwakanga kune wainzi Bharabhasi, akasungwa navamwe vakanga vamutsa mhirizhonga naye, vakanga vauraya pamhirizhonga iyoyo.
\v 8 Zvino chaunga chakadanidzirisa, vakatanga kukumbira \add kuti avaitire\add* sezvaaisivaitira.
\v 9 Asi Pirato akavapindura, achiti: Munoda kuti ndikusunungurirei Mambo wavaJudha here?
\v 10 Nokuti wakanga achiziva kuti vapristi vakuru vakanga vamukumikidza \add kwaari\add* negodo.
\v 11 Asi vapristi vakuru vakamutsa chaunga, kuti zviri nani avasunungurire Bharabhasi.
\v 12 Pirato akapindura akatizve kwavari: Zvino munoda kuti ndi\add mu\add*itireiko, wamunoti ndiMambo wavaJudha?
\v 13 Vakadanidzirazve \add vachiti\add*: Murovere!
\v 14 Asi Pirato akati kwavari: Nemhaka yei? Wakaita chakaipa cheiko? Vakanyanyisa kudanidzira \add vachiti\add*: Murovere!
\p
\v 15 Zvino Pirato, achida kufadza vanhu vazhinji, akavasunungurira Bharabhasi; asi wakakumikidza Jesu, a\add mu\add*rova netyava, kuti aroverwe.
\s Jesu unodadirwa namauto
\p
\v 16 Zvino mauto akamuisa mukati moruvanze, rwunova imba yomubati, akaunganidza hondo yose;
\v 17 vakamupfekedza zvine ruvara rwehute, vakaruka korona yemhinzwa, vakamudzika.
\v 18 Vakatanga kumukwazisa, \add vachiti\add*: Hekanhi, Mambo wavaJudha!
\v 19 Vakamurova musoro norutsanga, vakamupfira, vakafugama mabvi, vakamunamata.
\v 20 Zvino vakati vamusweveredza, vakamubvisa zveruvara rwehute, ndokumupfekedza nguvo dzake, vakaenda naye kundomurovera.
\s Jesu unoroverwa pamuchinjikwa
\p
\v 21 Vakamanikidza mumwe waipfuura \add wainzi\add* Simoni muKurini, achibva kuruwa, baba vaArekizandiro naRufo kutakura muchinjikwa wake.
\p
\v 22 Vakamuisa kunzvimbo \add yainzi\add* Gorogota, ndokuti kana zvichishandurwa: Nzvimbo yedehenya.
\v 23 Vakamupa waini yakavhenganiswa negavakava kuti amwe, asi haana kugamuchira.
\v 24 Zvino vakati vamurovera, vakagovana nguvo dzake, vachikanda mijenya pamusoro padzo, kuti mumwe nomumwe uchatorei.
\v 25 Yakanga yava nguva yechitatu, vakabva vamurovera.
\v 26 Norugwaro rwemhosva yake rwakanga rwakanyorwa pamusoro, \add ruchiti\add*: MAMBO WAVAJUDHA.
\p
\v 27 Pamwechete naye vakarovera makororo maviri, mumwe kuruoko rworudyi rwake, nomumwe kuruboshwe.
\v 28 Rugwaro rukazadzisika, rwunoti: Wakaverengwa pamwechete navadariki.
\p
\v 29 Navaipfuura vakamunyomba, vachidzungudza misoro yavo, vachiti: Haiwa, Iwe, unoputsa tembere, noku\add i\add*vaka namazuva matatu,
\v 30 zviponese, uburuke pamuchinjikwa!
\v 31 Saizvozvo vapristi vakuru vakamusweveredza pamwe navanyori pakati pavo, \add vachiti\add*: Wakaponesa vamwe, haagoni kuzviponesa.
\v 32 Kristu Mambo wavaIsraeri ngaaburuke ikozvino pamuchinjikwa, kuti tione titende. Navakanga varoverwa pamwechete naye vakamunyomba.
\v 33 Zvino nguva yechitanhatu yakati yasvika, rima rikavapo panyika yose kusvikira panguva yepfumbamwe.
\v 34 Zvino nenguva yepfumbamwe, Jesu akadana nenzwi guru, achiti: "Eroi, Eroi, rama Sabhakitani!" Ndokuti, kana zvichishandurwa: Mwari wangu, Mwari wangu, mandisiyireiko?
\v 35 Vamwe vavakanga vamirepo vakati vachi\add zvi\add*nzwa, vakati: Tarirai, unodana Eria.
\v 36 Ipapo mumwe wakamhanya, akazadza chipanje nevhiniga, akaisa parutsanga, akamupa kuti amwe, achiti: Regai, timboona kana Eria achizouya kumuburusa.
\v 37 Ipapo Jesu akadanidzira nenzwi guru akabudisa mweya wake.
\p
\v 38 Vheiri retembere rikabvaruka kuita \add mapandi\add* maviri, kubva kumusoro kusvikira pasi.
\v 39 Zvino mukuru wezana wakanga amirepo pakatarisana naye, wakati achiona kuti wadanidzira akapa mweya, akati: Zvirokwazvo, munhu uyu wanga ari Mwanakomana waMwari.
\p
\v 40 Kwakanga kune vakadziwo vakatarira vari kure, pakati pavo kwakanga kuna Maria Magidharini, naMaria mai vaJakobho muduku naJose, naSarome,
\v 41 (avo vaimutevera achiri muGarirea, vachimushandira), navamwe vakadzi vazhinji vakanga vakwira Jerusarema naye.
\s Kuvigwa kwaJesu
\p
\v 42 Zvino kwavira, zvarakanga riri gadziriro, ndokuti zuva rinotangira sabata,
\v 43 Josefa weArimatia, gurukota rairemekedzwa wakanga akamirirawo ushe hwaMwari wakauya akapinda kuna Pirato akatsunga, akakumbira chitunha chaJesu.
\v 44 Pirato akashamiswa nokuti wakanga atofa; akadana mukuru wezana, akamubvunza kana akanga ava nenguva afa.
\v 45 Zvino wakati a\add zvi\add*nzwa nomukuru wezana, akapa Josefa chitunha.
\v 46 Akatenga mucheka wakapfava, akamuburusa, akamuputira nemucheka, ndokumuradzika mubwiro hwakanga hwakacherwa paruware, ndokukungurusira ihwe pamukova webwiro.
\v 47 Zvino Maria Magidharini, naMaria \add mai\add* vaJose, vakaona paakavigwa.
